---            ---
--OpenCalc 0.0_2--
---            ---

OpenCalc is open-source calculator for GNU/Linux.


Instruction Manual:

Four options available in this version for calculating.

(1) for addition,
(2) for subtraction,
(3) for multiplication,
(4) for division.

Please select 1, 2, 3 or 4 numbers for calculate anything you want. You can only calculate
two number in this version.


--Installation--

make

- If you enter this command, source will be compiled.

make install (Under Construction)

- If you enter this command, software will be installed to /usr/bin directory.

NOTE: "make install" command not working in this version.


--News--

1- Added addition and subtraction. (Goal Achieved)
2- Fixed some issues.


--Goals for 0.0_3--

1- Adding "make install" option.
2- Adding more than two number calculating option.


